# >(_:_:)

**Operator**

Returns a Boolean array that indicates whether the corresponding element of a column type is greater than a value.

## Declaration

```swift
static func > (lhs: Self, rhs: Self.Element) -> [Bool]
```

## Return Value

A Boolean array.

## Discussion

- lhs: A column type.
- rhs: A value of the same type as the column.
